data.description: Discover the perfect fusion of serene country living and urban convenience in this captivating rural property, just minutes east of downtown Cheyenne. Completed in 2021, this home seamlessly combines main floor living with a newly finished basement, tailor-made for a home theater experience. Situated on a sprawling 5-acre parcel, this property offers endless opportunities for outdoor activities and the possibility of keeping animals.  VA Assumable Loan: VA buyers utilizing their own entitlement can take advantage of an assumable loan at an attractive rate of 2.75%.
